Title="Madehiten - Mountains of Secret"

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="It looks like the Krall are preparing the surroundings for the attack of the Skaarj. They currently have a secret base on the planet Exploited. Who knows what kind of sinister plans they brew."
M_NewMessage="Jadjis' notes"
M_TransMessage="Jadjis' notes"

[SpecialEvent7]
Message="Me: Thanks so much for information. I'll do what I can."

[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="Here in the mountains a few of us live. Old Mystic Spire is abandoned for decades. But three days ago, I noticed a glow in there. A day later the attack came. This morning two people from another planet were here, trying to warn us. So I went with them to the village."
M_NewMessage="Notes"
M_TransMessage="Notes"

[TranslatorEvent0]
Message="The Krall are coming from Mystic Spire for two days already. Jadjis, a friend of Hadan should know, where they are really coming from."
M_NewMessage="Notes"
M_TransMessage="Notes"

[TranslatorEvent4]
Message="After the travel today, I am pretty tired. I will rest for a while. Jadjis told me about the Stargate. He also advised me how to use it and gave me the address of the planet Exploited."
M_NewMessage="Message from your companion"
M_TransMessage="Message from your companion"

[SpecialEvent0]
Message="Jadjis: Welcome stranger. Hadan told me you were coming."

[TranslatorEvent64]
Message="My Log: Yet another bridge. It looks as stable as the first."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent63]
Message="My Log: What is this? I have never seen such crazy dressed people anywhere."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent62]
Message="My Log: Storage room. I should look for some equipment."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent61]
Message="My Log: So I'm in a basement. The spire is certainly not far away."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent60]
Message="My Log: Gosh. It is not a very nice feeling to cross the bridge made of planks and see somewhere far into the depths. I estimate a 1km deep chasm. I would not want to fall down."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent59]
Message="My Log: It's somewhat cozy here. I'll look in the next room, if the friend of Hadan is there."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent58]
Message="My Log: There is another house in the background. Perhaps there will be Hadan's friend."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent57]
Message="My Log: Fire. Just would be of use. I need to heat up a little, I am quite cold from being in that temple for so long."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent56]
Message="My Log: So I finally arrived at the mountains. I did not anticipate that my way will be limited to narrow cliffs. I'll have to walk carefully."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[SpecialEvent6]
Message="Jadjis:  Help the local people to defeat them. Now go. Good luck."

[SpecialEvent5]
Message="Jadjis:  The way you can get to the planet Exploited, which is currently occupied by the Krall."

[SpecialEvent4]
Message="Jadjis:  On the control panel there, you will dial this address."

[SpecialEvent3]
Message="Jadjis:  You need to go there and fight your way to the Stargate."

[SpecialEvent2]
Message="Jadjis:  They are still coming from Mystic Spire."

[SpecialEvent1]
Message="Jadjis:  As you already know, we were ambushed by the Krall yesterday."
